<http://www.spektrix.com/tarragontheatre/event/33201AJLRJQTMSPLGKHLNMPSPGHMNLTRH>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Night Logan Woke Up";
  schema:description """
	<h1><span class=\"BoldText\">The Night Logan Woke Up</span></h1><span><br/></span>Written by Michel Marc Bouchard<span><br/></span>Translated by Robert Chafe<span><br/></span>Directed by Jillian Keiley<span><br/></span>English-Language World Premiere<span><br/></span>A Co-Production by Tarragon Theatre, Artistic Fraud of Newfoundland, and Resource Centre for the Arts Theatre<span><br/></span>Mainspace<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>November 17 - December 13, 2026<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>As a girl, Emilia Lynch would cheat insomnia by slipping into neighbouring houses to spy on people as they slept, including her childhood crush Logan Goodyear. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Now, many years later, Emilia— an internationally renowned embalmer to the rich and famous— has returned to her small Newfoundland town following the death of her mother. As she prepares for the funeral alongside her three brothers, a shocking revelation is unearthed in her mother’s will; the final devastating consequence of the night Logan woke up. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Surreal, daring, and darkly funny, <span class=\"ItalicText\">The Night Logan Woke Up</span> is one of Bouchard’s finest works, making its long-awaited English language world premiere.  <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">\"★★★★ Michel Marc Bouchard delivers a masterful performance with a hard-hitting script.\" </span><span><br/></span>-La Presse<span><br/></span>
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-11-17T19:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/tarragontheatre/files/e416bbaa-fb43-4691-be9a-2dbaae8a5660.jpg>;
  schema:location <https://spektrix.com/tarragontheatre/location/801ARDQDDMGGJKKRTNTJBMCCMMBCPQKCR>;
  schema:organizer <https://spektrix.com/tarragontheatre/organization/tarragon-theatre>;
  schema:offers _:57e8ee661ad740a08e5ad0ea20bc4b346659;
  schema:duration "PT60M";
  schema:endDate "2026-11-17T20:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime .

